<section id="difference" class="px-6 py-20 md:py-28 border-t border-border">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
		<p class="eyebrow text-center">The blind spot</p>
		<h2 class="heading-lg text-center mt-3">Google traffic is shrinking.<br/>AI traffic converts 5× better.</h2>
		<p class="body-lg text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4">Gartner predicts a 50% decline in organic search traffic by 2028. The traffic is moving to AI answers — and AI answers cite sites that are optimized for extraction, not just ranking.</p>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-14">
			<div class="card p-8 border-red/20">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
					<span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-muted flex items-center justify-center text-red text-xs font-bold">✗</span>
					<span class="text-sm font-semibold text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider">Without AEOrank</span>
				</div>
				<ul class="space-y-3.5 text-sm text-text-muted">
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-red/60 shrink-0">✗</span>Invisible to ChatGPT, Perplexity, Claude — competitors get cited instead</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-red/60 shrink-0">✗</span>No llms.txt, no ai.txt — AI crawlers have zero context about your site</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-red/60 shrink-0">✗</span>GPTBot and ClaudeBot blocked by default in most hosting configs</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-red/60 shrink-0">✗</span>Content structured for Google snippets, not AI extraction</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-red/60 shrink-0">✗</span>No way to measure, track, or prevent AI visibility regressions</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-red/60 shrink-0">✗</span>Paying $129+/mo for a dashboard that only monitors — doesn't fix</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-red/60 shrink-0">✗</span>No way to show clients or stakeholders how your brand compares in AI answers</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="card p-8 border-accent/20">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
					<span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-green-muted flex items-center justify-center text-green text-xs font-bold">✓</span>
					<span class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent uppercase tracking-wider">With AEOrank</span>
				</div>
				<ul class="space-y-3.5 text-sm text-text">
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-green shrink-0">✓</span>Score 0–100 across 36 criteria — know exactly where you stand</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-green shrink-0">✓</span>9 AI-readable files auto-generated — llms.txt, ai.txt, schema.json, more</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-green shrink-0">✓</span>AI crawler access configured correctly — every engine, every bot</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-green shrink-0">✓</span>Content analyzed for AI extractability — not just SEO, but AEO</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-green shrink-0">✓</span>PR checks catch regressions before deploy — scores on every commit</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-green shrink-0">✓</span>Free, open source, self-hostable — no vendor, no lock-in, no bill</li>
					<li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-green shrink-0">✓</span>Shareable score report — show clients, stakeholders, or your board exactly where you stand</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
